[{"id":5863100010,"node_id":"LE_lADOAyxcHc5BaKXLzwAAAAFdd85q","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Homebrew/brew/issues/events/5863100010","actor":{"login":"colindean","id":197224,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5NzIyNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/197224?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean","html_url":"https://github.com/colindean","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"event":"labeled","commit_id":null,"commit_url":null,"created_at":"2022-01-10T01:49:38Z","label":{"name":"bug","color":"e10d02"},"performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Homebrew/brew/issues/comments/1008484281","html_url":"https://github.com/Homebrew/brew/issues/12689#issuecomment-1008484281","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Homebrew/brew/issues/12689","id":1008484281,"node_id":"IC_kwDOAyxcHc48HD-5","user":{"login":"colindean","id":197224,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5NzIyNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/197224?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean","html_url":"https://github.com/colindean","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2022-01-10T01:53:27Z","updated_at":"2022-01-10T01:53:27Z","body":"I've traced it down to how Ruby handles reading the output of `lsb_release` when it gets the release version information:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/Homebrew/brew/blob/7fc2159fcddd1deed70d2a7225d34750f080160b/Library/Homebrew/os/linux.rb#L14-L20\r\n\r\nwhich calls\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/Homebrew/brew/blob/7fc2159fcddd1deed70d2a7225d34750f080160b/Library/Homebrew/utils/popen.rb#L8-L13\r\n\r\nIn Ruby 2.7 installed from distro repos:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\na = IO.popen(\"lsb_release -a\", \"r\")\r\nl = a.readlines\r\np l\r\np l.map(&:encoding)\r\n```\r\noutputs:\r\n```\r\n[\"Distributor ID:\\tElementary\\n\", \"Description:\\telementary OS 6.1 J√≥lnir\\n\", \"Release:\\t6.1\\n\", \"Codename:\\tjolnir\\n\"]\r\n[#<Encoding:UTF-8>, #<Encoding:UTF-8>, #<Encoding:UTF-8>, #<Encoding:UTF-8>]\r\n```\r\n\r\nbut\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\na = IO.popen(\"lsb_release -a\", \"rb\")\r\nl = a.readlines\r\np l\r\np l.map(&:encoding)\r\n```\r\nOutputs:\r\n```\r\n[\"Distributor ID:\\tElementary\\n\", \"Description:\\telementary OS 6.1 J\\xC3\\xB3lnir\\n\", \"Release:\\t6.1\\n\", \"Codename:\\tjolnir\\n\"]\r\n[#<Encoding:ASCII-8BIT>, #<Encoding:ASCII-8BIT>, #<Encoding:ASCII-8BIT>, #<Encoding:ASCII-8BIT>]\r\n```\r\n\r\nRuby's JSON encoder tries to convert the ASCII-8BIT string to UTF-8 and fails because that's dangerous.\r\n\r\nAs I said in the linked issue on the `homebrew-bundle` repo, _a_ solution may be to force the encoding _or_ not read this particular call in binary mode (`popen(cmd, 'r')` instead of `'rb'`) when we're expecting UTF-8 data.","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Homebrew/brew/issues/comments/1008484281/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"colindean","id":197224,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5NzIyNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/197224?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean","html_url":"https://github.com/colindean","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"id":5863146192,"node_id":"REFE_lADOAyxcHc5BaKXLzwAAAAFdeILQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Homebrew/brew/issues/events/5863146192","actor":{"login":"colindean","id":197224,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5NzIyNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/197224?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean","html_url":"https://github.com/colindean","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/colindean/starred{/own