_read` but this may be the first thing to trigger it since\r\nJSON requires UTF-8 output and nothing else using that function may require UTF-8.\r\n\r\nFixes #12689\r\nFixes Homebrew/homebrew-bundle#1043\r\n\r\n- [X] Have you followed the guidelines in our [Contributing](https://github.com/Homebrew/brew/blob/HEAD/CONTRIBUTING.md) document?\r\n- [X] Have you checked to ensure there aren't other open [Pull Requests](https://github.com/Homebrew/brew/pulls) for the same change?\r\n- [X] Have you added an explanation of what your changes do and why you'd like us to include them?\r\n- [ ] Have you written new tests for your changes? [Here's an example](https://github.com/Homebrew/brew/blob/HEAD/Library/Homebrew/test/PATH_spec.rb).\r\n- [ ] Have you successfully run `brew style` with your changes locally?\r\n- [ ] Have you successfully run `brew typecheck` with your changes locally?\r\n- [ ] Have you successfully run `brew tests` with your changes locally?\r\n\r\n-----\r\n\r\nI verified this works on my own installation. I'll add some tests if maintainers think this is an acceptable way to fix this.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Homebrew/brew/issues/12690/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Homebrew/brew/issues/12690/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"id":5865856424,"node_id":"CE_lADOAyxcHc5BaKXLzwAAAAFdod2o","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Homebrew/brew/issues/events/5865856424","actor":{"login":"MikeMcQuaid","id":125011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEyNTAxMQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/125011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/MikeMcQuaid","html_url":"https://github.com/MikeMcQuaid","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MikeMcQuaid/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MikeMcQuaid/following{/other_user}","gi